column2: select Artist.Name as ArtistName, Track.Name, Track.UnitPrice, Album.Title from chinook.Track inner join chinook.Album on chinook.Track.AlbumId = chinook.Album.AlbumId inner join chinook.Artist on chinook.Album.ArtistId = chinook.Artist.ArtistId group by Track.Name, Track.UnitPrice, Album.Title, Artist.Name
